text: Crossotus vagepictus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fairmaire in 1886.BioLib.cz - Crossotus vagepictus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. It contains the varietas Crossotus vagepictus var. niveicollis. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1886
title: Crossotus vagepictus
